Notes:
17-year old Juniper Slouber flew his 54mm minimum diameter "Snake Are No More" to an awesome 26,989' on a K300 at XPRS 2017, Black Rock
Desert NV. Juniper is a TRA Junior Member, flying in the Tripoli Mentoring Program (http://www.tripoli.org/TMP) under Jonathan Dubose
(AeroPAC).  The Tripoli records committee congratulates Juniper on his outstanding achievement. Photos: Chris Atteberry
